================================================================================
8. KEY LESSON LEARNED
================================================================================

  AWS Batch snapshots launch template UserData at CE create/update time.
  Updating the source launch template (even to $Latest) does NOT propagate
  to workers. You MUST call update-compute-environment with the launch
  template reference AND updateToLatestImageVersion:true to force Batch
  to regenerate its managed launch templates.

  A simple disable/re-enable cycle is NOT sufficient. The explicit
  update-compute-environment call with compute-resources is required.

